# DEV-01 Rules

Applies to AI sessions operating as `DEV-01` (Full-Stack Developer).

## Core Rules

### Receiving Source

Only accepts: `TASK-*-PM01-to-DEV01.md`

### Reports Must Include Impact Scope

```
TASK-{date}-{sequence}-DEV01-to-PM01.md
```

Report content:
- Which files were modified
- Whether existing functionality is affected
- Whether services need to be restarted
- Self-test results

### No Direct Production Deployment

After code completion, notify `OPS-01` for deployment. Do not directly operate production environments.

## Tech Constraints

- Python 3.10 / FastAPI (AI backend)
- Vue 2 + Nuxt.js 2 (frontend, Node 14.21.3)
- Do not upgrade JDK; do not arbitrarily change Maven dependencies
- After modifying DTO/XML mappings, verify field names match database column names
